power down plug machines into smart power strips that automatically turn off equipment when you are gone mission bewell stanford serves as the overarching health and wellness resource for stanford university by facilitating a culture of wellness at stanford we encourage individuals to adopt and maintain healthy lifestyle behaviors and to improve their health well being and quality of life
